        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "[EV-002B] Skill Workshop parity: path, TOCTOU, prompt-budget hardening",
        "body": "## Summary\n\nImplements **EV-002B** (Skill Workshop defense-in-depth) per Evolves plan: gated procedural writer stays **only** in `extensions/skill-workshop`; no core `skills_manage` tool.\n\n### Changes\n- **G2 path:** `isPathInside` / `isPathInsideWithRealpath` from `openclaw/plugin-sdk/security-runtime` (re-export from `scan-paths`) for skill dir, SKILL.md, and support files.\n- **G3 TOCTOU:** Second `prepareProposalWrite` immediately before `atomicWrite`; stale workspace throws `skill proposal stale: workspace changed before write`.\n- **G4 economics:** `enforceSkillsPromptBudgetIfConfigured` uses `previewSkillsPromptImpact` / `buildSyntheticWorkspaceSkillEntryForPreview` (exported via `skills-runtime`) so queue and apply align with core skills prompt limits.\n- **Docs:** `docs/plugins/skill-workshop.md` — security model, memory vs Workshop, maintenance grep note.\n- **Tests:** pending no disk write, quarantine no SKILL.md, replace drift, POSIX symlink escape (`it.skipIf(win32)`).\n\n### Not in this PR\n- Research / learning-bridge telemetry on Workshop apply (deferred per EV-002B plan).\n\n### Validation\n- `pnpm test -- extensions/skill-workshop/index.test.ts` (23 tests)\n- `pnpm plugin-sdk:api:gen` + `pnpm plugin-sdk:api:check`\n\n### Notes\n- `resolveWorkspaceSkillPromptState` return type extended with `truncated`, `compact`, `skillsInPromptCount`, `skillsEligibleForPromptCount` so `previewSkillsPromptImpact` matches upstream `main` after merge.",
